TestRunDownstreamVariableAnnotatesAsResults
/ test.run write-target's downstream annotation must read (results), not
/ (object). Stage 2 typed test.run as Task<Data<Results>> — the reflected
/ return type carries through goal.getTypes into the next step's snapshot.
- builder.goals from 'probes/run/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- set %annot% = %snapshot[2].r%
- assert.equals expected='results', actual=%annot%
